Module ChessTournament
Package ntnu.idatt2001.k2g9.gui.models

Class TournamentModel

java.lang.Object
ntnu.idatt2001.k2g9.gui.models.TournamentModel
public class TournamentModel extends Object
Class that represents a Tournament. This is solely used to add data to the table, used in "AdminManageTournaments". This should not be confused with the actual Competitor object, which represent an actual competitor in the chess tournament.
